3.71},{"content":"合平家一门之力 定要诛杀赖朝","from":1194.07,"location":2,"to":1197.8},{"content":"虽然免去了流放","from":1201.19,"location":2,"to":1203.02},{"content":"但身为我们兄长 这实在是颜面尽失","from":1203.24,"location":2,"to":1205.69},{"content":"别丧气","from":1205.99,"location":2,"to":1206.88},{"content":"待我等出阵的时候","from":1207.18,"location":2,"to":1209.31},{"content":"定要威武果决地堂堂一战","from":1209.63,"location":2,"to":1211.88},{"content":"莫怕","from":1224.23,"location":2,"to":1225.41},{"content":"你真可爱","from":1227.21,"location":2,"to":1228.45},{"content":"我是琵琶","from":1229.09,"location":2,"to":1230.29},{"content":"维盛…","from":1246.59,"location":2,"to":1247.61},{"content":"你平安…","from":1250.71,"location":2,"to":1251.68},{"content":"我怕","from":1253.14,"location":2,"to":1253.89},{"content":"一想到那么多士兵攻来","from":1255.78,"location":2,"to":1258.57},{"content":"就怕得不行","from":1259.84,"location":2,"to":1260.77},{"content":"维盛","from":1264.86,"location":2,"to":1265.66},{"content":"今晚我想再看看你的舞","from":1265.98,"location":2,"to":1268.19},{"content":"就像严岛那次一样 在海边","from":1268.53,"location":2,"to":1270.69},{"content":"还要什么舞","from":1272.16,"location":2,"to":1272.94},{"content":"连都城都改换了","from":1273.9,"location":2,"to":1275.01},{"content":"我也必须改头换面","from":1276.04,"location":2,"to":1277.43},{"content":"我要战斗","from":1279.99,"location":2,"to":1281.04},{"content":"我必须战斗","from":1281.51,"location":2,"to":1283.18},{"content":"身为平家武士去战斗","from":1283.44,"location":2,"to":1284.82},{"content":"即便心里拒绝 耳朵总会听见","from":1311.82,"location":2,"to":1313.89},{"content":"荣华与没落 一代代地流传","from":1313.89,"location":2,"to":1315.84},{"content":"地狱 极乐 苦涩 甘甜","from":1315.84,"location":2,"to":1317.86},{"content":"精舍的钟声 听着已很遥远","from":1317.86,"location":2,"to":1319.76},{"content":"讲起道理总是鬼话连篇","from":1319.76,"location":2,"to":1321.58},{"content":"上面 下面 里面 外面","from":1321.58,"location":2,"to":1323.66},{"content":"世间常态是沧海桑田","from":1323.66,"location":2,"to":1325.29},{"content":"所有一切都已是梦幻","from":1325.29,"location":2,"to":1327.32},{"content":"凋落 崩溃 